<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
once you have a pet you get this window with buttons to control you pet.  One button will say "attack" click it when you have a mob targeted and your pet will go and attack it.<P>Quick cast appears in your ability menu and you have to turn it into an icon in your quick bar.  Click on it while you are being hit by a mob and it will allow you to cast your next spell while being hit.  However you are only allow to cast quickcast once per 20~ some seconds (don't remember the exact number) so choose carefully which spell you want to cast.  <P>I hope these were the answers you were looking for.
</FONT>
