New strategy in effect: They stated in the latest patch that a dex debuff will make the Monster(MOB) take more damage:  Hence, i now pull with my dex debuff, run back out of the "highway" of mobs and have my pet attack:<P>If you maintain a good distance from the MOB and are not right up on them. You can then dot and nuke to your hearts content.<P>Note* This is a new twist to the spec nobody really uses... doubling up on the dex debufs and a pet would mean oranges are now yellow???<P><BR>Belgarion 18 Sorcerer<BR>Galatan 19 Paladin
