Yes Thiebear, when I solo I always double up on the dex debuffs and I find that taking oranges is about as difficult for me as taking yellows is for most other classes, i.e. always win barring an additional mob joining the fray and downtime to heal/med back up. Yellows to me, on the other hand, are like blues to everyone else, i.e. 100% success rate, very little downtime.<P>--------------------<P>Nemus Imzadi <BR>Saracen Sorcerer <BR>Knight of Virtue<BR>Champions of Virtue, Bedevere <BR>www.championsofvirtue.com
